      <title>特朗普回归，中国抢购廉价巴西大豆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/china-is-snapping-up-cheap-brazilian-soybeans-as-trump-returns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在人们对中美贸易紧张局势加剧的担忧日益加剧之际，中国买家正在大举购买即将收获的巴西大豆，趁着价格诱人之际，此举也将有助于保障供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/china-is-snapping-up-cheap-brazilian-soybeans-as-trump-returns</guid>
